Who is Rammstein anyway? I know they are a German band, but have never heard their music...

 
 It's German metal. I would have to say that most of their songs fall under the category of "angry music", but that's not to say they aren't awesome. You've probably heard their popularized song "Du Hast" or "Feuer Frei" (if you've seen XXX - if you haven't, please don't). Their best songs are probably "Tier", "Sonne", "Sehnsucht", "Zwitter", "Engel", and "Ich Will". They're known mostly for their live shows (pyrotechnics). Check them out.
